      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elmhurst%2C_Queens"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "The former Elks Lodge Number 878, built 1923‑24, now houses a historic church and is on the National Register.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
